desc=Oh! You already reached level 5? Faster than I thought. Do you know what the sea is? Uh? Just the sea? Hahaha! You don't know what it is... The sea has something to allure you with. 
 An unknown continent, unknown people, unknown treasures... How exciting all of that sounds!  You will also experience this feeling. 
 Ah, I forgot you are a beginner. Your next task is related to the sea. You... do you have a ship? No? Just as I expected. Then I'll lend you one of mine which I don't use any more. I'm not too fond of it, but it has an average performance. 
 Now, you should confirm the ship before you set sail. Go to the dock and confirm your ship's current condition there.  Right-click on the shells in your inventory to equip them as well. Try it and come back to me. 
runDlg=What? You don't remember where to confirm your ship? Poor memory. I'll let you know again. Click on me and press the 'Dock' button among buttons shown at the bottom of the conversation. There you can confirm your ship. Remember it well, I won't tell you again. 
finishDlg=Did you confirm the ship? Is it better than you think? Hahaha, I gave it to you because of your behavior. Anyway I don't need it. But I don't do anything without a reason. If you don't get my respect, the ship will be dumped. Keep up the good work. Then I will let you know about my request. 
