desc=Ah... we're out of food, but I can't go get more right now. Hey, could you catch and bring me some 'Filefish'? Just a few! 
 You wonder how to catch them? Fishing is the best way. You say that you don't know how to fish? Uhm... So, why don't you learn it? It's easy. 
 First, you need to learn the way of the fisherman. Have you ever learned a land skill? It's just like that. You can buy the manual 'Directory of Fishing' to learn the skill. The point is that you only need to use one skill point for fishing. Once you have done that, go and fish after you have equipped a fishing rod and a bait. Got it? Sounds simple, doesn't it? Then good luck to you. 
runDlg=Fishing is possible wherever you want, but only inshore. Go to the beach and fish. I'll be waiting here. 
finishDlg=Getting items while fishing is quite charming. There you go, this is your reward. Thank you for your help. 
