</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Delivering Rice to Clouds 
desc=Hellow! We are heading towards Clouds, but we're short of helping hands and there's too much work to do. Why don't you help us? How? All you need is a ship! You do have a ship, don't you? 
 What you need to do now is that you need to deliver 'Rice' to an island named 'Clouds' nearby. Then, you have to give the rice to the 'Clouds Trade Owner'. 
 He will then give you a specialty from 'Clouds' and then, you have to give this to me. It isn't as complicated as you might think now. Build up stocks of 'Rice' now on your ship. Good luck to you! 
runDlg=Clouds' is located in northern direction from the entrance of the harbor. When pressing key 'M' key, you can see it on the map. Have a safe journey.
finishDlg=Come here. Are you from 'Roxbury'? I have been waiting for you. This island is quite small, so we often run out of 'Rice'. 
