</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Delivering Olive oil to Jeremiah 
desc=Now, this is 'Olive oil'. Please give this to Jeremiah. 'Olive oil' is the specialty of Clouds Island. It is selling at a high price in Roxbury. If you have enough Gelt to purchase it, you should think about selling it in Roxbury, as you can make a lot of money by trading. It's merely a question of time. Never heard about trading? I'll give you an example. 

 Rice can't grow up here. So we pay more for our rice than those in Roxbury. If you sell rice to me, you'll make a profit. On the contrary, you can purchase 'Olive oil' here and sell it at a higher price in Roxbury. You'll eventually get rich doing this. It's called the trade system. 
 But something to be cautious of is that if you sell 'Olive oil' in Roxbury, the value of 'Olive oil' decreases with more oil available. You then won't make a profit. So you always need to keep an eye on the fluctuation of the market price based on the current price, so you don't incur a loss. 
 Think about it. And now, please deliver the 'Olive oil'. 
runDlg=When you keep an eye on the fluctuation of the market price, you avoid losing money and you make a profit. You should always check the prices twice. 
finishDlg=You did a good job. Thank you for delivering the 'Olive oil'. It feels good to make such great deals with Clouds Island. 
</newversion></questtextxml></systuto04><systuto05><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Seagull &#xD1F4;&#xCE58;
