</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Exterminating Seagulls 
desc=A serious thing happened and we suffered a loss. Do you want to know what happened? There is a group of plunderers that assault several trade ships. They are not exactly a group, as they appear here and there. But they plunder ships no matter where, so they need to be exterminated. 
 The captain of a ship that has recently been plundered says he knows where they are going next. The direction is to the east of Cardiff Island. Perhaps you'll meet them if you follow these instructions. 
 Please help us by exterminating the 'Seagulls', so we can continue to trade safely. But you shouldn't confront them alone. You should better fight against them together with other people. You can guess there will be quite a reward due to the difficulty of this task. 
runDlg=Rumor has it that the 'Seagulls' went to the harbor and traveled to the east of Cardiff Island. If you go to the east, you'll find them. 
finishDlg=Thank you! I had already heard the news before you arrived. All merchants said they are really thankful, just as I am. Please help us next time as well if the same thing happens again. 
