desc=I think we haven't met before. You ready for some adventures? There is a suitable request for beginners. But... do you know how to use weapons?  Florensia is more dangerous than you think. You should be able to protect yourself. I'll teach you the basics of survival. The first thing you have to learn is how to equip and change weapons. Let's start by opening your inventory. If you press the 'I' key, you can open your inventory. Now you need to take a weapon. Double-click on the 'Tutorial Cariad' to equip it. You should see that your character holds it. Please equip the 'Tutorial Rapier' in the same way. If you want to change weapons during battle, you can change the weapon slots by pressing the 'R' key or 'F1, F2, F3' on your keyboard. Now, equip the weapons and change the equipped weapon.
preDlg=There is an urgent request. Right-click on me and press the 'Quest' button. 
runDlg=If you think about what you want, it shouldn't be difficult at all. Practice makes perfect.
finishDlg=Excellent! You are already good at handling your weapons. I think you are ready for the next task. First, I'll give you your payment. And if you complete a quest, you can receive Gelt or items according to the difficulty. There's still some things left for you to learn.
