Mission2=Using Land skill points
desc=You learned how to equip and change weapons and the use of lethal techniques is up next. We call them 'skills'. If you use 'skills', you can perform stronger attacks or make use of various abilities during a battle. Now, you need to learn new 'skills' with the skills book located in inventory. You can use your skills after you have spent at least 1 skill point on them. Remember this part, will you. Whenever you level up, you will gain 1 skill point. Enough of the theory, you should go practice now. Come back once you have learned your skills.
runDlg=It's difficult to learn skills from the scratch. As previously stated, there is no difficulty if you do it slowly and correctly. 
finishDlg=You're learning quickly. There are only few people who were so fast. Also, there are many more powerful or helpful skills aside the ones you've just learned. I think you can make good use of such powerful skills. But there's something else you need to know.
