desc=Now I will let you know how to quickly use your skills. The bar you see at the lower right corner of the screen is your 'quick slot' bar. If you drag and drop skills on the bar and press the according numbers shown within the cells, you will use the according skills. Using the quick slot bar is very convenient, because you can also put other items from your inventory there. Take a look at the 'Minor Tutorial Powder' in your inventory. Drag skills and this powder onto your quick slot bar. 
runDlg=Choose an item or a skill you want to have on your quick slot bar by left-clicking on it. Drag the selected icon on the quick slot bar, then left-click on the slot where you want to place it. The skill or item will be added to your quick slot bar. 
