desc=As I said before, I will let you know about the contents of the request. I heard that monsters have come near to the entrance of our village, Roxbury. Fortunately, they are only 'Weak Fungis'. Nevertheless, there are many inconveniences whenever the villagers travel. I request you to hunt 'Weak Fungis'. 'Weak Fungis' can be found beyond the east gate of the village. If you press 'M' on the keyboard, the map for the entire village or the field appears, So you can check where you're heading. It may be easy thing to hunt 'Weak Fungis'. Go and practice what you've learned so far. Complete the request, and I'll give you the promised reward. 
runDlg=Weak Fungis are east of the entrance to Roxbury. You can find them there easily
finishDlg=Excellent! They are weak enemies, but I thought you might have difficulties encountering a large number of them. Your future looks bright. The next request won't be a problem for you either.
