desc=Go to the dockyard in the southeast of Roxbury and meet Mr.'Stephen'. Whoever wants to set sail needs his help first. Fortunately, he has a request which you can complete. I already told him about you, so you can go straight to him without hesitating. Don't worry about it and deal with the request. If you are acquainted with him, I think you'll get a lot of help. Make an effort to satisfy him and you may go to the sea right away. 
